title: Container Wars - 01.13.2013 - Boom or Bust - WEB-DLx264.JIVE.mp4
description:
Container Wars: Boom or Bust (?) - aired on or around January 13, 2013.

Description: Containers up for auction have asian spices, automobile parts and vintage americana, with another having possible martial arts equipment.


*This is 1 of the 2 missing episodes from 1st half of the first season*

Note: because of lack of description, I've been unable to dtermine an episode number from TVRage.  However, it's very possible that's the episode number 1x2 (production number 105) with the title "Matt Attack".

The capper had named it "Boom or Burst"; which would make it the episode 1x1 based on Amazon.com but in my opinion, this is most likely the episode 1x2.
